Case Name: Delete project

Triggering Event:

User selects button to delete a project.

Scenario Description:

User presses button 'delete project'. 

Main Actor(s): Admins

Precondition(s):

A project exists and has been created by the user who wants to delete it.

Post condition(s):

A project is deleted and does not exist anymore. User lands at 'projects page'.

Main Path:

. User clicks on a specific project she wants to delete
. Selects and clicks 'delete project' button
. Pop up page with text such as 'Confirm you want to delete this project'
. User clicks on confirmation button
. Project is deleted
. User is back at the page with all project

Alternative Path:
TBA
